But voli isn't a god of war, he is a sage. and there are already multiple gods of war walking around.{{champion:266}} {{champion:80}} 

and you mention the retcon a lot, but what you probably don't know that the retcon officially ignored the freljord event, the shurima event, and the bilgewater event which all took place at around the same timeframe, because all of those events had little to do with the lore of the summoners.
